title: (Mon Part 2) The Draft: Things from the 2000’s + We Reveal Our Greatest High School Moments!
itunes:title: (Mon Part 2) The Draft: Things from the 2000’s + We Reveal Our Greatest High School Moments!
description:
Per listener request, we bring back the drafts! Today, we all drafted the best things from the 2000’s! There was a crazy story about a high schooler doing a backflip during a basketball game…so we all reveal our one biggest thing that we’d remember forever from high school. We also share the ONE Jason Aldean song we could buy from his catalogue after his sells for $100 million.
